# TheWing.ai

TheWing.ai is the SaaS intelligence layer for PCSUnited.

PCSUnited is the public military resource hub for PCS, pay, PT, housing, VA loans, base intelligence, and military family guidance.

TheWing.ai powers the advanced decision tools inside PCSUnited, including financial dashboards, AI guidance, housing intelligence, BuyerBrief workflows, readiness scoring, and future realtor-by-base intelligence.

## Brand Role

PCSUnited gets the eyes.  
TheWing.ai powers the decisions.

## Core Modules

- Financial Analysis Dashboard
- Housing Intelligence Dashboard
- Ask Amy AI Guidance
- BuyerBrief Engine
- Affordability Scoring
- Realtor-by-Base Intelligence
- Saved User Profile Tools
- Advanced PCS Decision Briefs

## Build Rule

This repository is not a rebrand rabbit hole.

Its purpose is to house the advanced software layer for PCSUnited so the public PCSU site can remain clean, useful, and SEO-focused.
